    "CODE LLMS, SOFTWARE QUALITY AND TRUSTWORTHINESSThe use of LLMs in automatic programming shows immense potential.",
    "However, this progress brings with it concerns about the trustworthiness of the code these models produce.",
    "For instance, Jesse et al. [65] found code LLMs tend to Authors introduce simple bugs in the codebase.",
